Comment.value:
Vengaul and his men are on one side of a cavern crevice. When the players arrive, he has been yelling at Callik from across the gap. An infotrigger at the edge can say there was a bridge here, but it's been destroyed.

While the players fight Callik, Vengaul and his men lob arrows into the fray, mostly at Callik and his men, but the occasional one will be for the player, accompanied by a "sorry."

After this dialogue or during it, Vengaul or one of his men place a crate on the ground. Its the Cockatrice and they then leave. Player has to go a short distance around to get the crate.
his men attack while he leaves.
